{"arkId":"cl010364524","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010364524","modified ":"2025-12-10","title":"Service \u00e0 th\u00e9","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Service \u00e0 th\u00e9"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine) ; Monarchie de Juillet (1830-1848) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1826 - 1838","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 561 - Duc d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans","room":"Salle 561, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1826,"endYear":1838,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Odiot, Charles Nicolas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1789","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1869","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q12981883"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12159","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; service","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Ce service \u00e0 th\u00e9 est compos\u00e9 de dix-neuf pi\u00e8ces (notamment une fontaine \u00e0 th\u00e9, deux th\u00e9i\u00e8res, une bo\u00eete \u00e0 th\u00e9, deux pots \u00e0 cr\u00e8me\u2026), conserv\u00e9es dans le coffre d\u2019origine, aux armes des Montmorency-Laval : chiffre ML, encadr\u00e9 de la devise \u0022DIEU AIDE AU PREMIER BARON CHRESTIEN\u0022. Il provient vraisemblablement d\u2019Anne-Adrien-Pierre de Montmorency-Laval (1768-1837), qui \u00e9tait \u00e0 la fois pair de France et Grand d\u2019Espagne, puisqu\u2019on trouve sur ses armoiries le collier du Saint-Esprit et une toison d\u2019or. \r\nL\u2019influence anglaise, caract\u00e9ris\u00e9e par des formes pansues et godronn\u00e9es, des th\u00e9i\u00e8res en forme de melon, s\u2019explique par le s\u00e9jour de formation d\u2019Odiot aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019orf\u00e8vre londonien Robert Garrard. La veine naturaliste se borne dans ce service \u00e0 des prises en fleurs pour les th\u00e9i\u00e8res et les sucriers, une anse v\u00e9g\u00e9tale pour le beurrier ou un d\u00e9cor de vigne pour la pince \u00e0 sucre.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Chiffre : ML des Montmorency-Laval, encadr\u00e9 de la devise DIEU AIDE AU PREMIER BARON CHRESTIEN\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Fabricant (O, une lampe antique allum\u00e9e); Paris, argent, 1819-1838, 1er titre et grosse garantie","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":"","shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent (dor\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Probablement Anne Adrien Pierre de Montmorency-Laval (1768-1837), duc de Laval et pair de France, duc de San-Fernando-Luis et grand d\u2019Espagne ; acquisition par arr\u00eat\u00e9 du 12 novembre 2004.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"10\/11\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"12\/11\/2004","startYear":2004,"endYear":2004}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"period":[{"value":"Restauration (1814-1830)"},{"value":"Monarchie de Juillet (1830-1848)"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"service"},{"value":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Dion, Anne, Orf\u00e8vrerie fran\u00e7aise du XIX\u00e8me si\u00e8cle. La collection du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Paris, Louvre \u00e9ditions \/ Somogy, 2011","bibliographyDate":"2011","bibliographyDetail":"p. 224-225, n\u00b0 109","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010105927","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010105928","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113207","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113209","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113397","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113398","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113399","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113400","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113401","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113402","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113403","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113417","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113418","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113419","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113420","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113421","type":"Contient"},{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113422","type"